            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 10 月 24 日消息，机械革命极光&nbsp;16&nbsp;笔记本现已在京东上架，<strong>这款游戏本采用“i7-13620H + 16GB RAM + 1TB&nbsp;储存空间&nbsp;+ RTX4060”配置，售价为 6499&nbsp;元，将于 10 月 31 日开售</strong>。</p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/M6faViH" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/245274/6/21134/159039/6718a94dF3a409d80/e7d4d346b0cb01e6.jpg" title="机械革命极光 16 游戏本上架：i7-13620H + 16G + 1T + RTX4060 售 6499 元" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">机械革命极光 16 笔记本</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 6499 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1332" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/f14ebb0a-f5c3-4eee-888f-6c079bc8a368.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="机械革命极光 16 游戏本上架：i7-13620H + 16G + 1T + RTX4060 售 6499 元" width="732" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1198" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/2de32002-ed76-48fa-a7ad-ba4c08641009.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="机械革命极光 16 游戏本上架：i7-13620H + 16G + 1T + RTX4060 售 6499 元" width="720" /></p><p>外观方面，这款笔记本 A 面采用航空级镁铝合金，配备&nbsp;RGB&nbsp;键盘，整体厚度约&nbsp;24mm。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="936" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/cd0e0b7f-14b6-4dab-bf6d-606e33e33941.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="机械革命极光 16 游戏本上架：i7-13620H + 16G + 1T + RTX4060 售 6499 元" width="710" /></p><p>该机搭载&nbsp;10&nbsp;核心&nbsp;16&nbsp;线程&nbsp;13&nbsp;代英特尔酷睿&nbsp;i7-13620H&nbsp;处理器，内置&nbsp;16GB DDR5 4800MHz RAM&nbsp;及&nbsp;1TB PCIe 4.0 SSD，采用双风扇&nbsp;6&nbsp;铜管&nbsp;4&nbsp;出风口散热设计。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1150" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/dd1d0984-dcbe-4f48-b63d-c50011d59699.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="机械革命极光 16 游戏本上架：i7-13620H + 16G + 1T + RTX4060 售 6499 元" width="710" /></p><p>此外，IT之家获悉该机配备一块&nbsp;16&nbsp;英寸&nbsp;2560x1600&nbsp;分辨率&nbsp;165Hz&nbsp;屏幕，覆盖&nbsp;100% sRGB&nbsp;色域。</p><p>这款笔记本支持&nbsp;Wi-Fi 6，机身左置&nbsp;1&nbsp;个&nbsp;USB-A 3.2 Gen 2&nbsp;接口、1&nbsp;个 3.5mm&nbsp;音频接口；右置&nbsp;2&nbsp;个 USB-A 3.2 Gen 1&nbsp;接口、1&nbsp;个 SD&nbsp;卡读卡器；后置&nbsp;1&nbsp;个 mini-DP&nbsp;接口、&nbsp;1 个 USB-C&nbsp;接口、1&nbsp;个&nbsp;HDMI 2.1&nbsp;接口、1&nbsp;个 RJ 45 接口。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="596" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/ca3ff514-dcdc-4fe0-9740-a10d33bbb9ca.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="机械革命极光 16 游戏本上架：i7-13620H + 16G + 1T + RTX4060 售 6499 元" width="718" /></p><p>2024 年 11.11 大促全网好价合集：<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fcontentlist%3Fapi%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnapi.ithome.com%252Fapi%252Ftopmenu%252Fgetmenufeeds%252F166%252F0%252Fnone%252F0%26title%3D2024%25E5%258F%258C11%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BF%2583%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E9%2580%2589%26mode%3D0" target="_blank" title="点此查看">点此查看</a></p><p><span class="font-color-red"><strong>京东无门槛红包&nbsp;</strong></span>至高 11111 元：<a href="https://u.jd.com/CaQySbH" target="_blank" title="点此抽今日红包"><strong>点此抽今日红包</strong></a></p><p><span class="font-color-orangered"><strong>天猫无门槛红包&nbsp;</strong></span>至高 24888 元：<strong><a href="https://s.click.taobao.com/w26hFPt" target="_blank">点此抽今日红包</a></strong></p><p><span class="font-color-purple"><strong>唯品会无门槛红包</strong></span> 至高1111元：<a href="https://t.vip.com/VbMVne" target="_blank"><strong>点此抽今日红包</strong></a></p><p><br /></p><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p>
